data.description: Just shy of an Acre! This Unique Waterfront Property is located on Florida's Scenic Indian River Drive and has 85 ft+/- of private sandy beach, pilings standing ready for a dock, which once restored, will make the perfect place to park your boat, and the land on the waterside of the property, has potential for sweeping views of Florida's Intracoastal Waterway, Hutchinson Island and enough space to park your water toys.The home, built in 1920's, although magnificent in its time, is in disrepair and will need to be torn down, making way for you to build that waterfront compound you have been waiting for on a well established ''old Florida''property within a mile from downtown Fort Pierce.
